aVBlack Sales Agents Sue Xerox, Accusing It of Bias Current and former black sales representatives of Xerox sued the company, accusing it of racial discrimination and retaliation. The suit, which seeks class-action status, echoes charges filed earlier this year with the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission by former and current Xerox sales representatives who contended they were discriminated against on the basis of race. [Page C4.]
